gw.api.builder

Class AccountLocationBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<AccountLocation,AccountLocationBuilder>
      • gw.api.builder.AccountLocationBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<AccountLocation>

    public class AccountLocationBuilder
extends DataBuilder<AccountLocation,AccountLocationBuilder>
    Builder class for creating a new AccountLocation. The simplest usage is 
       new AccountLocationBuilder().createAndCommit()
    which creates a AccountLocation with some default values.
